                    </div>
                    <span>Mr. Morris' book is inspiring.  I read the original Prince by Machiavelli, but it was inconclusive and difficult to apply to today's democratic standards (although there are some things that will never change).  This book can be applied in all stations and situations of life, for all of these are relative.<br>     I believe that this is, truly, a guide to people--not just politics.  It is a worthwhile read.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Want to survive in workplace and get ahead?</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
